The,service,provides,a,scaled,view,of,the,horizon,and,terrain,from,a,specified,location,defined,as,a,map,point,on,Google,Maps,It,calculates,a,viewshed,from,the,location,based,on,local,terrain,contours,and,depicts,a,view,from,the,location,highlighting,mountains,in,the,distance,It,is,intended,to,answer,questions,like,Hey,what,s,that,when,viewing,a,horizon,API,methods,support,submission,of,a,location,either,as,a,panorama,query,or,as,a,latitude,longitude,Methods,adjust,for,day,and,time,and,for,atmospheric,refraction,which,changes,the,view,of,distant,terrain,due,to,bending,of,light,through,air